query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
address as "address!: String", 
block_number as "block_number!: Decimal", 
block_hash as "block_hash!: String", 
tx_hash as "tx_hash!: String", 
tx_index as "tx_index!: Decimal", 
log_index as "log_index!: String", 
data as "data!: String", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime" FROM synced_events WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR address = $4::varchar) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR block_number = $6::decimal) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR block_hash = $8::varchar) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR tx_hash = $10::varchar) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR tx_index = $12::decimal) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR log_index = $14::varchar) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR data = $16::varchar) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR created_at = $18::timestamptz) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($19 = 'Id' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Id' AND $20) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Address' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN address ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Address' AND $20) WHEN true THEN address ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'BlockNumber' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN block_number ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'BlockNumber' AND $20) WHEN true THEN block_number ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'BlockHash' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN block_hash ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'BlockHash' AND $20) WHEN true THEN block_hash ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'TxHash' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN tx_hash ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'TxHash' AND $20) WHEN true THEN tx_hash ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'TxIndex' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN tx_index ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'TxIndex' AND $20) WHEN true THEN tx_index ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'LogIndex' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN log_index ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'LogIndex' AND $20) WHEN true THEN log_index ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'Data' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN data ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'Data' AND $20) WHEN true THEN data ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($19 = 'CreatedAt' AND NOT $20) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($19 = 'CreatedAt' AND $20) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $21 OFFSET $22 FOR UPDATE
